Comparison Between the Joins
 
                      Advantage          Probe Memory Component   Data Set Sizes    Requires Equijoin   cons
					  
Nested loop joins    Better response            No                Small data sets       NO             no large data sets
Hash Joins           Better throughput			Yes				  Large data sets       Yes            More PGA
Sort Merge Joins     Better throughput          Yes               Large data set        NO             Sorting is expensive
